---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Testimonials" description="Hear from clients who have worked with Severino Realty.">
  <section class="py-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">What Our Clients Say</h1>
    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-8">We pride ourselves on delivering outstanding service. Here are a few words from our valued clients.</p>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="bg-neutral-100 p-6 rounded-md shadow-sm">
        <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-2">“Severino Realty made the home buying process stress‑free. Their agents were knowledgeable and patient, guiding us from start to finish.”</p>
        <p class="font-semibold text-primary">– James &amp; Sarah, Karen</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-neutral-100 p-6 rounded-md shadow-sm">
        <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-2">“I listed my apartment with Severino and received several serious inquiries within days. Their marketing is top notch!”</p>
        <p class="font-semibold text-primary">– Amina, Kilimani</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-neutral-100 p-6 rounded-md shadow-sm">
        <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-2">“Professional, transparent and friendly. I highly recommend them for both rentals and purchases.”</p>
        <p class="font-semibold text-primary">– Michael, Westlands</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
